A1: new roles and responsibilities for staff
RelatedSentence: The complex structure of the new NHS - and the role of the GPs - have meant new roles and responsibilities for staff in the English health services .
In a Daily Politics film with Richard Murray of the Kings Fund , Giles Dilnot explains the changes introduced by Heath Secretary Jeremy Hunt and his predecessor Andrew Lansley .
